Metadata: Pacific Sea Grant Advisory Program Inventory of marine resources publications and films
Pacific Sea Grant Advisory Program through Oregon State University Sea Grant Marine Advisory Program

This publication is an inventory of printed and audio-visual material on marine resources that is available from the six western universities participating in the Pacific Sea Grant Advisory. The six are: University of Alaska, University of British Columbia, University of Hawaii, Oregon State University, University of California, and the University of Washington. Th​e directoryt is divided into three sections in the following order: publications, films, and supplementary bibliographies.
